remarks: Emendation & homonym;  Homonym of Lioptilus Cabanis, 1850 (Aves)

Note: This species was published in: Heinrich, 1921: 827, dd. Mar. 1st, 1921. and later on Aug. 31st, 1921, again by the same authors. The misspelling of the genus name has occured in the original publication
